desc_short	-----								Dive into the vast world of retro motorsport racing. Multiple game modes, diverse vehicles, hundreds of tracks, online and local multiplayer for up to 6 players, single player and super smooth gameplay guarantees a thrilling racing game. Finally, make your own race tracks with the included track editor!							
